### Promotion Filter API Tests

### 1. Get all promotions (basic test)
GET http://localhost:8080/api/promotions


### 2. Filter promotions - no filters (get all with pagination)
GET http://localhost:8080/api/promotions/filter?page=1&size=10

### 3. Filter by search (code or description)
GET http://localhost:8080/api/promotions/filter?search=SUMMER&page=1&size=10

### 4. Filter by status (active promotions)
GET http://localhost:8080/api/promotions/filter?status=active&page=1&size=10

### 5. Filter by promotion type (coupon type)
GET http://localhost:8080/api/promotions/filter?type=coupon&page=1&size=10

### 6. Filter by promotion type (auto type)
GET http://localhost:8080/api/promotions/filter?type=auto&page=1&size=10

### 7. Filter by minimum discount value
GET http://localhost:8080/api/promotions/filter?minDiscount=10&page=1&size=10

### 8. Filter by maximum discount value
GET http://localhost:8080/api/promotions/filter?maxDiscount=50&page=1&size=10

### 9. Filter by discount range
GET http://localhost:8080/api/promotions/filter?minDiscount=5&maxDiscount=25&page=1&size=10

### 10. Filter by start date (promotions starting after this date)
GET http://localhost:8080/api/promotions/filter?startDate=2025-01-01&page=1&size=10

### 11. Filter by end date (promotions ending before this date)
GET http://localhost:8080/api/promotions/filter?endDate=2025-12-31&page=1&size=10

### 12. Filter by date range
GET http://localhost:8080/api/promotions/filter?startDate=2025-06-01&endDate=2025-08-31&page=1&size=10

### 13. Complex filter - multiple conditions
GET http://localhost:8080/api/promotions/filter?search=summer&status=active&type=coupon&minDiscount=10&maxDiscount=50&startDate=2025-01-01&endDate=2025-12-31&page=1&size=10

### 14. Filter with different page sizes
GET http://localhost:8080/api/promotions/filter?page=1&size=5

### 15. Filter second page
GET http://localhost:8080/api/promotions/filter?page=2&size=5

### 16. Filter by status - expired promotions
GET http://localhost:8080/api/promotions/filter?status=expired&page=1&size=10

### 17. Filter by status - inactive promotions  
GET http://localhost:8080/api/promotions/filter?status=inactive&page=1&size=10

### 18. Search with partial match
GET http://localhost:8080/api/promotions/filter?search=giảm&page=1&size=10

### 19. Search case insensitive
GET http://localhost:8080/api/promotions/filter?search=DISCOUNT&page=1&size=10

### 20. Filter with no results (should return empty list)
GET http://localhost:8080/api/promotions/filter?search=nonexistentpromotion&page=1&size=10

